'''Articles of Secession''' were the proclamations issued by various [[Planet/Legends|planetary]], [[Star system/Legends|systematic]], and [[Sector/Legends|sectorial]] governments during the [[Separatist Crisis/Legends|Separatist Crisis]] and the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] that declared intentions to leave the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] and join the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederacy of Independent Systems]].

